Class Importer

  • java.lang.Object
    • ie.gmit.sw.Importer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Parserable

    public class Importer
extends java.lang.Object
implements Parserable
    This class is manages the creation of a list of ordered words. You can pass in a file or url to create a ordered list of words. You can create a blacklist for those ordered words to keep common words out.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Andy Sweeney - G00237144
